original_title: 13 Levels of Pumpkin Carving: Easy to Complex
overview: Pumpkin carving master James Hall explains pumpkin carving in 13 spooky levels of difficulty. The 2-time 'Halloween Wars' winner breaks down a variety of pumpkin carving techniques, ranging from simple to incredibly complex.
title: 13 Levels of Pumpkin Carving: Easy to Complex
